                    </span>
                    WhatsApps</a>
            </ul>
        </span>

        <span class="footer-center">
            <h3 class="network-title"><span class="icon">
            </span><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i>
            Ou sommes-nous ?</h3>
            <p class="footer-text">31 Route du Ruisseau
            <p class="footer-text">Batiment A,</p>
            <p class="footer-text">Toulouse, </p>
            <p class="footer-text">31000</p>
        </span>

